name: Solberg
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: With the goal to make investing in the future of decentralized finance (DeFi) easy and accessible to everyone, Solberg mission is to empower people to access decentralized finance (DeFi) and easily transfer to the Solana blockchain with minimal efforts. Through Solberg we decided to show all of the benefits of using decentralized finance (DeFi) and Solana Platform.
